'''Govan Archibald Mvuyelwa Mbeki''' ([[July 9|9 July]] [[1910|1910]] - [[August 30|30 August]] [[2001|2001]]) ebele  [[Mopolotiki|molotiki]] wa [[Afrika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]], ele motswadi wa [[Thabo Mbeki|Thabo Mbeki]], mopresidente wa [[Afrika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]].  Govan o theilwe morago Edward Govan, "Scottish missionary" o a thomilego [[Lovedale (South Africa)|Lovedale College]], sekolo seo a bego a tsena gosona.

O tsene sekolo [[Fort Hare University|Fort Hare University]], a phetha dithuto ka  [[1936]] (Bachelor of Arts degree - [[Politics|Politics]]) le  [[Psychology|Psychology]] mmogo le diploma ya go ruta. 

Ebile moeta pele wa [[African National Congress|African National Congress]] (ANC) le [[South African Communist Party|South African Communist Party]]. Morago ga [[Rivonia Trial|Rivonia Trial]], o ile a golegwa ke mmušo wa kgale wa [[Afrika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]]([[1964|1964]]–[[1987|1987]]) le [[Nelson Mandela|Nelson Mandela]], [[Walter Sisulu|Walter Sisulu]] le baetapele ba bangwe ba ANC. 

Ka  [[June 26|26 June]], [[1980|1980]] mongwaledi kakaretšo wa [[African National Congress|African National Congress]], Alfred Nzo, o begile gore Govan Mbeki o tla fiwa [[Isitwalandwe Medal|Isitwalandwe Medal]], tlotla ye kgolokgolo ya ANC. Govan Mbeki o be a sa golegile [[Robben Island|Robben Island]]ka nako yeo.

Govan Mbeki o tšwele kgolegong morago ga go dula mengwaga ye masome pedi nne (24) ka [[November 5|5 November]] [[1987|1987]].


